Production mai Kafka almost hamesha partitions ki copies (replicas) multiple brokers par rakhi jaati hain.

Ye Kafka ka Replication concept hai.

Without Replication

Maan lo:

'Orders' Topic is having 3 partitions:

Partition-0 -> Broker-1
Partition-1 -> Broker-2
Partition-2 -> Broker-3

Diagram:

+-------------------+
| Broker-1          |
| Partition-0       |
+-------------------+

