Production systems me ye issue hota tha.

Isliye Kafka ne later:

Cooperative Rebalancing

introduce ki.

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Cooperative Rebalancing Kya Hai?
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Purana approach:

Sab partitions chhodo
Sab dobara assign karo

Naya approach:

Sirf zaruri partitions move karo

Example:

Pehle:

P0 -> C1
P1 -> C2
P2 -> C1

C3 join hua.

Purana rebalance:

Sab revoke karo
Sab dobara assign karo

Naya cooperative rebalance:

P2 -> C3

Bas.

Baaki assignments disturb nahi hote.

Production me ye preferred approach hai.

