13 : ISR (IN SYNC REPLICAS)
===============================================================================

ISR (In Sync Replicas) Kafka ke fault tolerance ka core concept hai.

Maan lo Kafka cluster me multiple brokers hain:

Broker-1
Broker-2
Broker-3

Topic = Alphabet

Topic ke paas sirf 1 Partition hai:

Partition-0

Aur Replication Factor = 3 hai.

Matlab Partition-0 ki total 3 copies (replicas) hongi jo different brokers
par store hongi.

Partition Distribution:

Broker-1 -> Partition-0 (Leader)

Broker-2 -> Partition-0 (Follower)

Broker-3 -> Partition-0 (Follower)


                 Partition-0

            Leader (Broker-1)
                   |
          -------------------
          |                 |
          v                 v

 Follower (Broker-2)   Follower (Broker-3)

------------------------------------------------------------
MESSAGE FLOW
------------------------------------------------------------

Producer message bhejta hai:

"A"

Sabse pehle message partition-0 ke Leader Replica (In Broker-1) ke paas jayega.

Leader:

Offset 0 -> A

Uske baad Followers (In Broker-2 and Broker-3) Leader se data copy karenge.

Follower-1:

Offset 0 -> A

Follower-2:

Offset 0 -> A

Ab teeno replicas same state me hain.

Producer aur messages bhejta hai jo ki partition-0 ke Leader replica (In Broker-1) mai sequentially store hote hai:

Leader:

Offset 1 -> B
Offset 2 -> C
Offset 3 -> D

Uske baad Followers Leader se data copy karenge.

Current State:

Leader: (In Broker-1)

Offset 0 -> A
Offset 1 -> B
Offset 2 -> C
Offset 3 -> D

Follower-1: (In Broker-2)

Offset 0 -> A
Offset 1 -> B
Offset 2 -> C
Offset 3 -> D

Follower-2: (In Broker-3)

Offset 0 -> A
Offset 1 -> B
Offset 2 -> C
Offset 3 -> D

Ab teeno replicas completely synchronized hain.

------------------------------------------------------------
ISR KYA HAI?
------------------------------------------------------------

ISR (In Sync Replicas)is a set of replicas that are in sync with the leader.

Current State:

Leader (In Broker-1)       Offset 3
Follower-1 (In Broker-2)   Offset 3
Follower-2 (In Broker-3)   Offset 3

ISR:

ISR = {Leader, Follower-1, Follower-2}

Note:

ISR sirf healthy aur synchronized replicas ka set hai.

Aur yaad rakho:

Leader bhi partition ki ek replica copy hi hai, bas usko special role mila hua hai, isliye leader bhi ISR ka member hota hai.

------------------------------------------------------------
OUT OF SYNC REPLICA
------------------------------------------------------------

Ab Producer aur messages bhejta hai jo ki partition-0 ke Leader replica (In Broker-1) mai sequentially store hote hai:

Leader: (In Broker-1)

Offset 4 -> E
Offset 5 -> F
Offset 6 -> G

Uske baad Followers (In Broker-2 and Broker-3) Leader se data copy karenge.

Lekin maan lo Broker-3 slow ho gaya.

Current State:

Leader:(In Broker-1)

Offset 0 -> A
Offset 1 -> B
Offset 2 -> C
Offset 3 -> D
Offset 4 -> E
Offset 5 -> F
Offset 6 -> G

Follower-1:(In Broker-2)

Offset 0 -> A
Offset 1 -> B
Offset 2 -> C
Offset 3 -> D
Offset 4 -> E
Offset 5 -> F
Offset 6 -> G

Follower-2:(In Broker-3)

Offset 0 -> A
Offset 1 -> B
Offset 2 -> C
Offset 3 -> D

Replica Lag:

Leader       Offset 6
Follower-1   Offset 6
Follower-2   Offset 3

Kafka observe karega ki:

Follower-2 Leader se kaafi piche chal raha hai.

Isliye Kafka usse ISR se remove kar dega.

New ISR:

ISR = {Leader, Follower-1}

Important:

Follower-2 ab bhi Replica hai.

Lekin ab wo ISR member nahi hai.

Yaani:

Total Replicas = 3

But

ISR Members = 2

Note: ISR me hone ka matlab ye nahi ki replica har moment leader ke exact same offset par hai. ISR replicas thoda lag kar sakte hain.

------------------------------------------------------------
Kafka ISR Maintain Hi Kyu Karta Hai?
------------------------------------------------------------

Current State:

Leader (Broker-1)

Offset 0 -> A
Offset 1 -> B
Offset 2 -> C
Offset 3 -> D
Offset 4 -> E
Offset 5 -> F
Offset 6 -> G

------------------------------------------------

Follower-1 (Broker-2)

Offset 0 -> A
Offset 1 -> B
Offset 2 -> C
Offset 3 -> D
Offset 4 -> E
Offset 5 -> F
Offset 6 -> G

------------------------------------------------

Follower-2 (Broker-3)

Offset 0 -> A
Offset 1 -> B
Offset 2 -> C
Offset 3 -> D

------------------------------------------------

Replica Status:

Leader       -> Offset 6
Follower-1   -> Offset 6
Follower-2   -> Offset 3

ISR = {Leader, Follower-1}

Follower-2 leader se kaafi piche chal raha hai,
isliye wo ISR ka part nahi hai.

------------------------------------------------------------
Ab Maan Lo Leader Crash Ho Gaya
------------------------------------------------------------

Leader Broker-1 par tha aur crash ho gaya.

Ab Kafka ko naya Leader elect karna hoga.

Question:

Kafka kisko naya Leader banaye?

------------------------------------------------------------
Case 1: Agar Follower-2 Ko Leader Bana Diya Jaye
------------------------------------------------------------

Follower-2 ke paas sirf offset 3 tak ka data hai i.e

Offset 0 -> A
Offset 1 -> B
Offset 2 -> C
Offset 3 -> D

Lekin purane Leader ke paas offset 6 tak ka data tha i.e

Offset 0 -> A
Offset 1 -> B
Offset 2 -> C
Offset 3 -> D
Offset 4 -> E
Offset 5 -> F
Offset 6 -> G


Agar Follower-2 ko Leader bana diya gaya, to:

E, F aur G permanently lost ho sakte hain.

Matlab data loss ho gaya.

------------------------------------------------------------
Case 2: Agar Follower-1 Ko Leader Bana Diya Jaye
------------------------------------------------------------

Follower-1 Leader ke saath fully synchronized tha.

Uske paas bhi offset-6 tak ka data maujood hai.:

Offset 0 -> A
Offset 1 -> B
Offset 2 -> C
Offset 3 -> D
Offset 4 -> E
Offset 5 -> F
Offset 6 -> G

Isliye agar Follower-1 ko Leader promote kiya jaye,
to koi data loss nahi hoga.

------------------------------------------------------------
Conclusion
------------------------------------------------------------

Kafka ISR maintain karta hai taaki Leader failure ke time
sirf unhi replicas me se naya Leader select kiya jaye
jo Leader ke saath synchronized hain.

To ISR koi permanent group nahi hai.

Ye continuously update hota rehta hai based on replica health and lag.


