## Scenario 3

Current ISR:

{Leader, Follower-1}

Count = 2

Ab Producer aur messages bhejta hai.

Message Leader par write ho jata hai.

Lekin Follower-1 bhi crash ho jata hai ya Leader ke saath sync nahi reh pata.

Kafka Follower-1 ko bhi ISR se remove kar deta hai.

